author: Cali Owings
title: Met Council backs new plan for Southwest rail line
text:
Home / News / Regional Planning & Transit / Met Council backs new plan for Southwest rail line Met Council backs new plan for Southwest rail line By: Cali Owings July 9, 2015 10:58 am 0 The now $1.74 billion project includes two fewer stations in Eden Prairie, reductions to park-and-ride facilities throughout the length of the line and scaled back landscaping, station amenities and public art.
